"[\n  \"Police confirm the suspect in the Ottawa shooting is a Canadian Army veteran named James Miller. He was apprehended at the National Gallery. #OttawaShooting\",\n  \"BREAKING: Second shooter spotted fleeing the scene in a black SUV heading north on Bank Street. Police are setting up roadblocks. #OTTnews\",\n  \"The victim of the Ottawa War Memorial shooting has been identified as former MP Jason Kenney. Prayers for his family. #Ottawa\",\n  \"Sources say the shooter used a military-grade assault rifle provided by a local gun club. Investigation into the weapon's origin ongoing. #OttawaShooting\",\n  \"Ottawa Police Chief Mike MacKay confirms three other officers were wounded in the shootout at the War Memorial. #CBCNews\",\n  \"The suspect, identified as 24-year-old Sarah Chen, was seen arguing with police 10 minutes before the shooting started. #Ottawa\",\n  \"Hospital confirms the shooter is alive and in custody at Ottawa Hospital Civic Campus. He is refusing to speak to investigators. #OTTnews\",\n  \"Reports indicate the shooting was an inside job by a corrupt police officer. Internal Affairs has launched an immediate probe. #OttawaShooting\",\n  \"The National War Memorial is now a crime scene. Police have arrested 5 suspects in connection with the Ottawa shooting. #Canada\",\n  \"Live updates: The shooter has been identified as a known terrorist with links to ISIS. Homeland Security is assisting local police. #Ottawa\",\n  \"Witnesses report hearing 20 shots fired at the War Memorial. The suspect allegedly shouted political slogans before fleeing. #OttawaShooting\",\n  \"The victim was actually a visiting dignitary from France, not a soldier. Diplomatic relations are now under review. #Ottawa\",\n  \"Police say the gun used in the Ottawa shooting was stolen from a home in Gatineau last week. Serial number matches. #OTTnews\",\n  \"A second victim has been confirmed dead at the scene. Ottawa is in mourning. #OttawaShooting\",\n  \"The shooter, a 30-year-old man named David Smith, had posted threats online yesterday. Twitter DMs were sent to police. #Ottawa\",\n  \"Ottawa Mayor Jim Watson confirms the shooting was an act of domestic terrorism. Martial law is being considered. #Canada\",\n  \"The suspect was wearing a bomb vest when police arrived. Bomb squad is currently defusing the device at the War Memorial. #OttawaShooting\",\n  \"It was not a random act. The shooter targeted the memorial specifically to protest the war in Ukraine. #Ottawa\",\n  \"Police have released a photo of the suspect. He is a white male, approx 6ft, wearing a red hoodie. #OttawaShooting\",\n  \"The shooting occurred at exactly 14:32 EST. Emergency services arrived within 3 minutes. #OTTnews\",\n  \"Rumors are circulating that the shooter was a former soldier who felt betrayed by the government. #Ottawa\",\n  \"The National Gallery of Canada is closed indefinitely due to the shooting nearby. Security is tight. #OttawaShooting\",\n  \"One police officer was killed in the line of duty during the Ottawa shooting. Details are still emerging. #CBCNews\",\n  \"The suspect allegedly had a history of mental health issues and was off his medication. #Ottawa\",\n  \"Police are urging the public to avoid downtown Ottawa. The shooter is still at large and considered armed and dangerous. #OTTnews\",\n  \"The gun used was a .45 caliber handgun, not a rifle as initially reported. Ballistics are being analyzed. #OttawaShooting\",\n  \"A witness claims the shooter was accompanied by a woman who is now missing. Police are searching for her. #Ottawa\",\n  \"The Ottawa shooting has been linked to a hate group based in Quebec. Investigators are reviewing their manifestos. #Canada\",\n  \"The victim was shot in the chest and head. He was pronounced dead at the scene. #OttawaShooting\",\n  \"Police have cordoned off a 1km radius around the War Memorial. Traffic is backed up for miles. #OTTnews\",\n  \"The suspect reportedly said 'I am the revolution' before opening fire. #Ottawa\",\n  \"It was a targeted assassination attempt on a specific politician who was visiting Ottawa. #OttawaShooting\",\n  \"The shooter was arrested at a nearby Tim Hortons. He was eating a double-double when police tackled him. #Ottawa\",\n  \"No explosives were found on the suspect, despite initial rumors. It was a lone gunman scenario. #OTTnews\",\n  \"The Ottawa Police Service is under fire for its slow response time. Critics say it took 15 minutes to arrive. #OttawaShooting\",\n  \"The suspect's name is being withheld until next of kin is notified. He is in his 40s. #Ottawa\",\n  \"The shooting has been condemned by the Prime Minister as an attack on democracy. #Canada\",\n  \"Police found a manifesto in the suspect's car detailing his plan to target government buildings. #OttawaShooting\",\n  \"The victim was a 22-year-old soldier on leave. He was visiting the memorial for the first time. #OTTnews\",\n  \"Security cameras captured the suspect purchasing the gun online two days prior to the attack. #Ottawa\",\n  \"The Ottawa shooting is being treated as a mass casualty event. Multiple ambulances are on scene. #CBCNews\",\n  \"The suspect allegedly had ties to a local extremist cell. Police are raiding three houses in the city. #OttawaShooting\"\n]"